  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Dovecot</title>

    <para>
      <application>Dovecot</application> is an Internet Message Access Protocol
      (IMAP) et Post Office Protocol (POP) server, written primarily with
      security in mind. <application>Dovecot</application> aims to be
      lightweight, fast et easy to set up as well as highly configurable et
      easily extensible with plugins.
    </para>

    &lfs74_checked;

